        <date>1931 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The poster features two abstract figures. One appears to be playing an accordion, the other is holding out his hand like a beggar. The film title is printed above and below.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The feature ‘Istanbul sokaklarinda’ (In the streets of Istanbul) was a sound film – a Turkish-Egyptian-Greek co-production – released in 1931. It was directed by Muhsin Ertuğrul.</ab>
